These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
House: tower, palace, modern, colonial, cottage, craftsman
The people have 6 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, singing, skydiving, woodworking, writing
1. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the colonial house##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the tower house##1
4. the tower house is on the left of the modern house##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
7. the cottage house is on the right of the palace house##1
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the tower house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| House   | craftsman | tower  | modern    | colonial  | palace      | cottage    |
| Hobby      | puzzles  | writing | woodworking | gardening | skydiving | singing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: lilac, coral, ebony, orange, emerald, pink
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person who likes pink is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
9. the person who likes lilac is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Color   | lilac   | emerald | coral | pink | orange     | ebony  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, indie, punk, soul
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, blend, baccarat, aristoff, havana, bluemaster
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of soul##1
2. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of country is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
5. the fan of punk is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
7. the aristoff-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the baccarat-smoker is the fan of indie##1
9. the fan of country is the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | indie   | soul   | punk      | classical | blues  | country   |
| Cigar   | baccarat | bluemaster | alhambra | blend   | havana | aristoff |

