.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: blues, classical, country, disco, dubstep, indie
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: bellflower, azalea, zinnia, sunflower, balloon-flower, begonia
1. the person who growsbellflower is on the far left##1
2. the fan of country is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is the fan of disco##1
6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
7. the fan of dubstep is on the far right##1
8. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Music-Genre   | country  | disco | blues      | classical  | indie | dubstep |
| Flower     | bellflower | begonia  | balloon-flower | zinnia | sunflower  | azalea    |

