.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-5::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, hiking, singing, traveling, woodworking
City: nizza, new-york, hannover, hamburg, colone, berlin
 1. the person traveling to hannover is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |
| Hobby         | singing | woodworking | baking | traveling | filmmaking | hiking  |
| City   | berlin  | hamburg  | hannover  | nizza | colone      | new-york |

