3. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the fan of country##1
5. the game-smoker is the fan of pop##1
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of disco##1
9. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | dubstep    | country | indie     | disco   | folk     |
| Cigar   | game | swisher | bluemaster | bolivar | old-henry | davidoff |

