.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-7::.
There are 6 different nationalities: indonesian, malaysian, thai, argentine, turkish, british
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, roller, ship, snowmobile, trike
1. the indonesian is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the malaysian##1
3. the thai is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the argentine is the person driving the trike##1
6. the thai is the person driving the roller##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
8. the malaysian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |   3   |     4      |   5   |     6      |
| Nationality         | malaysian       | british     | argentine | thai | turkish | indonesian |
| Transport   | motorbike | snowmobile | trike | roller     | bike  | ship       |

