.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-8::.
There 6 different types of food: spinach, pear, pepper, tomato, grapes, strawberry
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, ice-hockey, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person eating pepper is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person eating tomato##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person eating pear##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating strawberry##1
6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
7. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
8. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |     3      |     4      |   5   |       6       |
| Food   | strawberry | spinach  | grapes     | pepper    | pear  | tomato          |
| Sport         | golf  | biathlon | ice-hockey | volleyball | rugby | weightlifting |

