.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
There 6 different types of food: broccoli, cranberry, kiwi, onion, peach, peas
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: april, february, september, january, november, may
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
6. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
7. the person eating peas is the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Food          | cranberry | peas   | peach  | kiwi    | onion  | broccoli |
| Birthday   | february   | april | may | november | september | january |

