.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-11::.
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, poker, snooker, domino, go
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, librarian, manager, pilot, writer
1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person playing go is on the far left##1
4. the librarian is on the right of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
6. the fisherman is on the far right##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is the manager##1
8. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
9. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |   3   |      4      |    5     |     6     |
| Game   | go    | mah-jongg     | poker | bridge | snooker | domino   |
| Job        | writer | manager | pilot | librarian   | coach    | fisherman |

