.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-12::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, december, august, april, september, february
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, jet-ski, motorbike, scooter, van
1. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
8. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
9. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |    5    |    6    |
| Birthday   | september | february | april    | december | august  | november |
| Transport     | bus    | scooter | motorbike | van   | jet-ski | bike    |

